text: Alexander Jesse Norman (born 23 June 1962) is a British Conservative Party politician. He is the Paymaster General and Financial Secretary to the Treasury since 2019, and has been Member of Parliament (MP) for Hereford and South Herefordshire since 2010. ==References== ==Notes== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Conservative Party (UK) MPs Category:Politicians from London Category:UK MPs 2010–2015 Category:UK MPs 2015–2017 Category:UK MPs 2017–2019 Category:UK MPs 2019–2024 Category:UK MPs 2024–present
